Package sailpoint.integration

Interface Summary
Authenticator An interface used by the IntegrationServlet to provide pluggable authentication.
HttpClient An HttpClient issues HTTP requests.
IntegrationInterface Interface that defines the methods that may be supported by an integrated provisioning system.
 

Class Summary
AbstractIntegration A base implementation of IntegrationInterface that stubs out most methods methods to throw exceptions.
ApacheHttpClient An implementation of HttpClient that delegates all calls to the Apache HTTP client.
AuthenticationUtil A utility to help perform authentication for REST requests.
Base64 Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
Base64.InputStream A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
Base64.OutputStream A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
Cryptographer Deprecated. This uses the old SailPoint default key - do not use this.
IIQClient Class providing a convenient interface for SailPoint IIQ web services.
IIQClient.AuthorizationService Helper class IIQClient.checkAuthorization(String, String).
IIQClient.AuthorizationService.CheckAuthorizationResult Encapsulates the result of checking authorization.
IIQClient.AuthorizationService.Consts Constants used by the authorization service.
IIQClient.IdentityService Helper class for identity create and update methods.
IIQClient.IdentityService.Consts Constants used for identity create and update.
IIQClient.IdentityService.Consts.AttributeNames JSON attributes in the POST request bodies to create and update an identity.
IIQClient.IdentityService.CreateOrUpdateResult Encapsulates the result or creating or updating an identity.
IIQClient.PasswordService Helper class used by IIQClient.checkPasswordPolicy(String, String).
IIQClient.PasswordService.CheckPasswordResult Encapsulates results from IIQClient.checkPasswordPolicy(String, String)
IIQClient.PasswordService.Consts Constants used for password policy checking.
IntegrationServlet An HttpServlet to convert a set of REST request into calls to an IntegrationInterface class.
JsonUtil Utility class for rendering and parsing JSON.
ListResult Transfer object that is used to send back a list of results which may be sorted and paged.
ObjectResult Simple RequestResult that returns a single object.
ProvisioningPlan Class used maintain a complex provisioning request involving several applications.
ProvisioningPlan.AccountRequest A request to modify a single account.
ProvisioningPlan.AttributeRequest A request to add, remove, or set the value(s) of an attribute on an object or account.
ProvisioningPlan.ObjectRequest A request for a non-account object (eg - a group).
ProvisioningPlan.PermissionRequest A request to add, remove, or set permissions.
RemoteIntegration Implementation of IntegrationInterface that uses REST resources to communicate with the provisioning system over HTTP.
RequestResult A RequestResult holds information about a request on an integration system.
RestClient Utility class for sending REST-style requests and parsing responses.
RestServlet An HttpServlet to handle REST requests.
RoleDefinition Class used to convey a role definition through the web-services interface to a provisioning system when we're doing role synchronization.
RoleEntitlement Class used to convey a role definition through the web-services interface to a provisioning system when we're doing role synchronization.
RoleResource Class used to convey a role definition through the web-services interface to a provisioning system when we're doing role synchronization.
SailPointHttpClient A custom implementation of HttpClient.
SailPointHttpClient.Cookie Helper class containing information about cookies.
TestAuthenticator An example authenticator that disallows any user names that start with 'X'.
TestIntegration Implementation of IntegrationInterface used for end-to-end testing of the integration framework.
TraceExecutor Implementation of IntegrationExecutor interface used for system testing.
Util Various utilities copied over from the sailpoint.tools package.
XmlUtil Utilities for creating and parsing XML.
XmlUtil.SailPointEntityResolver Custom entity resolver that handles different locations.
XmlUtil.SailPointErrorHandler Custom error handler that just throws exceptions.
 

Exception Summary
RestClient.ConnectionProblemException Exception indicating a connection exception.
